    "Abre Atajos y ve a la pestaña Automatización.\n\nToca + (Nueva automatización) y elige el gatillo Wallet.\n\nSelecciona tus tarjetas de Apple Pay y marca Ejecutar inmediatamente." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Open Shortcuts and go to the Automation tab.\n\nTap + (New Automation) and choose the Wallet trigger.\n\nSelect your Apple Pay cards and check Run Immediately."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Abre Xpense para empezar" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Open Xpense to get started"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Abrir Atajos" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Open Shortcuts"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Agrega tu primer gasto con el botón +, o configura la automatización de Apple Pay en Ajustes." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Add your first expense with the + button, or set up the Apple Pay automation in Settings."
