      }
    },
    "Xpense usa la app Atajos de Apple para enterarse de cada pago con Apple Pay y registrarlo en segundo plano, sin abrir la app.\n\nConfigurarlo toma unos minutos y se hace una sola vez." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Xpense uses Apple's Shortcuts app to find out about every Apple Pay purchase and log it in the background, without opening the app.\n\nIt takes a few minutes and you only do it once."
